data.description: Accepted Offer with Contingencies. Recently updated, this corner lot beauty has a new roof, newer hard-plank siding, vinyl double pane windows, and newer paint! Featuring 3 bedrooms, including a primary suite with a 1/2 bath, this home dazzles with an open living concept. The kitchen, living, and dining areas seamlessly blend for comfort living. A 2nd living area, complete with a fireplace, adds extra warmth and charm. Overlooking a large field and just blocks from Trader Joes this location offers privacy and comforts of amenities!
